Check the IPO draft against the checklist.

OUTPUT FORMAT (Markdown table)
Columns:
1) Checklist Item ID
2) Checklist Requirement
3) Status (Compliant / Partially Compliant / Missing / Non-Compliant)
4) Evidence From Draft (quote or excerpt; 1–3 sentences max)
5) Reference (doc_name | page/section if available; otherwise "Not provided")
6) Issue Explanation (1–3 sentences)
7) Suggested Remediation Text (2–5 sentences; must be consistent with checklist wording)

INPUTS
A) CHECKLIST ITEMS
<<CHECKLIST_ITEMS>>

B) IPO DRAFT CONTENT (with section/page metadata if available)
<<DRAFT_CONTENT_WITH_METADATA>>

C) OPTIONAL GUIDELINE EVIDENCE (if provided)
<<GUIDELINE_EVIDENCE_WITH_METADATA>>
